e clicking on the link then selecting download link to disk or save linked file note if you are having trouble viewing pdf documents in your browser try re installing the plugin if you have more than one browser program on your computer be sure to select the correct one when installing the plugin viewing flash movies in order to view the flash movies on this site you will need to have the adobe flash plugin installed in your browser most current browsers come with the plug in pre installed however if you are having problems viewing flash movies you will need to visit the adobe site to download and install the plugin changing the type size on your browser the stanford benefits site is set up so that you may change the type to whatever size is comfortable for you to read note that depending on the browser version you are using changing the type size might slightly affect the page layout we apologize for this inconvenience for windows users with firefox to change the type size in firefox select text size from the view menu this gives you the option to increase or decrease the type size for windows users with internet explorer press and hold down the control or ctrl button while moving the scroll wheel on your mouse this will increase or decrease the type size depending on which direction you move the scroll wheel for mac users firefox and safari both use the same method for changing type size hold down the command button also known as the apple button while pressing the plus or minus keys we do not recommend using internet explorer on the macos home benefits overview medical & life retirement resource library contacts mybenefits site map how to use this site human resources stanford university stanford university terms of use copyright complaints document download
